<lyrics>[V1]
 1- yạ syd ạ̉nt kl mạ ly slạmy fy dnyty qdny lṭryqy ạ̹ly̱ ạlạ̉bdyẗ fbrwḥk ạ̉qtdy
 fmạdẖạ trbḥy yạ nfsy lw ạlkwn bydk bʿryk lạ tstḥy dʿyh btẖwbh ystrk
 ạlqrạr- ḥyạty kmạ tryd ạ̉nt yạrb dbrhạ
 lạ ạ̉mlk swy̱ mqlạʿy bạsmk ḥrby tnṣrhạ
 lạ sẖk ạ̉bdaⁿạ fyk lạ̉nk ln tkẖdẖlny
 2- mrny fạ̉ṭyʿk mn mn qṭyʿk ḍl trkth bl tbdẖl dẖạtk tʿṭy ḥyạtk lsẖạh fqdth
 fạlạ̉rḍ klhạ tsẖdw lk rạʿy ḥnạn ạ̉nhạrhạ bḥwrhạ tsẖd lk ṭwl ạlạ̉zmạn
 3- ạtkl ʿlyk fmạ ạḥtyạjy lgẖyr brk ymynk trfʿny fy sqwṭy tkẖrjny lrḥbk
 tạ̉dybaⁿạ ạ̉dbtny wạ̹ly̱ ạlmwt lm tsmlny ạ̉sẖkrk lạ̉nny ṣkẖrt lk flm tkẖdẖlny</lyrics>
